\id 2JN
\ide  UTF-8
\h 2 John 
\toc1 2 John 
\toc2 2 John 
\toc3 2jn 
\mt1 2 John  
\c 1
\p
\v 1 Churji nindi iwandi a che ni wa u mirli wandi minyeme niba kpukpome ana hime ni kankirzi muwa, nibiwandi bato njanji.  
\v 2 Nitu njanji wandi kiheniwua anihe nita kasese.  
\v 3 Tibi ni malati, ni sisro, ba sonita ni rji ubati yeni yesu almasihu vreji ni inyi njanji ninyeme.  
\v 4 min ngyiri kpukpome niwandi mito imri me bari bazere ni miyi njaji niyu wandi kikpa ngwroyi nitimbu.  
\v 5 zizaa misi breu iyiko minasin ngya nwrosamambaniwuna iwayikife tunise tunturmu, ndikinyeme nikpambwu.  
\v 6 iwayi, i iwayimba binwro, abini wandi biwo in mumla, ndiduyi zere miyima.  
\v 7 bi gyurundi ba rju ni gbunblu biwandi banayeme ndi iverji ayenan diana ba babiandi ba gyrundi a nala nitingu ni vrerji.  
\v 8 ya kpambi, nahama ni kpe wandi kitindu tuma na yi, kpa sambi.  
\v 9 indyi wandi azerehini koshishi anahe myi nwro Almasihu na ana henirjina. iwandi a wonnwroa aheni tia-mba vre.  
\v 10 indyi wandiaynyi anakpawroyina, nakpa nikombina, nachi menayi.  
\v 11 mpempebi iwandi achia bati kyumban ni miyi memkppe wandi anitia.  
\v 12 mihenikpe gbugbwu iwandi misongya niwa u mbe ni-ma ungya na tsramena. tokimame misingyri soye kini treni kpanbu shishi mba shishi, nindu kinkiasrombu ndu shune.  
\v 13 imirli v vayime iwandi binyeme niwu bachiu.   